  <brief_title>Perioperative Chemotherapy Compared To Neoadjuvant Chemoradiation in Patients With Adenocarcinoma of the Esophagus</brief_title>
  <acronym>ESOPEC</acronym>
  <official_title>Perioperative Chemotherapy (FLOT Protocol) Compared To Neoadjuvant Chemoradiation (CROSS Protocol) in Patients With Adenocarcinoma of the Esophagus</official_title>
